text: Edward king gret wel Willem biscop & Leofwyne eorl & alle mine þeyngnes on Middelsexan frendlice.
& icc kyþe eou þat hit is min fulle unne þat Aylric hauet so gyfen þat land at Greneforde Crist ant Seinte Petre in to Westmenstre for þare forewarde þe þase broþera & he se maked habbað.
& icc ann heom þar to saca & socna, toll & theam, infangeneþef & alle þas rithe þe to me belunged.
